r\">\n      <p>\n        I'm a photographer drawn to quiet light &mdash; early mornings on the\n        coast, the last minutes of golden hour, the in-between moments people\n        don't pose for. I shoot landscapes, portraits, and the streets of\n        wherever I happen to be. Available for commissions and print inquiries.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n    <p>For bookings, prints, or just to say hello:</p>\n    <a class=\"email\" href=\"mailto:<email>\"><email></a>\n    <div class=\"socials\">\n      <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Instagram\">Instagram</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Flickr\">Flickr</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"500px\">500px</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</main>\n\n<footer>\n  &copy; 2026 {{userName}} &middot; All photographs are the property of the artist.\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"
